<div id="about-the-community" class="section-spacer">
    <h2 class="sect-title">About Airdrie Meadows</h2>
    <div class="col-grid-2">
        <div>
            <p class="par-lg">Airdrie is conveniently located at a distance of 6 kilometers from Calgary and is only a mere 20 minutes' drive from the Calgary International Airport. </p>
            <p class="par-lg">Owing to its friendliness and convenience, Airdrie Meadows Real Estate has attracted young families, north-east commuters, and a large number of working professionals. </p>
            <p class="par-lg">Homes for sale in Airdrie Meadows have an average list price of $284,000. </p>
            <p class="par-xl">From comfortable low-rise apartments to well-designed condos and townhouses, Airdrie Meadows provides everything a family would need for a comfortable living.</p>
        </div>
